761
00:36:32,750 --> 00:36:34,480
Dapat batiin 'yan.

762
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:37,840
Panginoong Yan.

763
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:39,760
Nag-iisip pa rin ang pamilyang Li

764
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,620
